Saudi Arabia cuts Dec crude to Europe 15 - 30 cts / bl . Saudi Arabia reduced term crude oil prices to European customers for December by 15 - 30 cents a barrel , U . S . trade sources said . The biggest drop in price was for Berri Extra Light , which fell 30 cents to Dated Brent minus $ 1 . 00 a barrel . Arab Light was cut 25 cents to Dated Brent minus $ 1 . 85 a barrel , and Arab Medium was cut by 20 cents to Dated Brent minus $ 3 . 05 a barrel . The price for Arab Heavy was dropped 15 cents to Dated Brent minus $ 3 . 60 a barrel , traders said . - - New York Energy Desk + 1 212 859 1620 
